  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink407">
<l>nayanta kātalit taḻīip pāṇar</l>
<l>nayampaṭu muraṟkaiyiṉ yātta payaṉṟerin</l>
<l>tiṉpuṟu puṇarcci nukaru</l>
<l>meṉpula vaippi ṉāṭukiḻa vōṉē</l>
      </lg>
    
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Embracing [his] desired beloved and </l>
<l>knowing the joy attached to the bard's desirable music,</l>
<l>the lord of the land with regions of soft fields</l>
<l>is experiencing a pleasurable union.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
